    "description": [
      "Large and small totems, some stacked as tall as a giantman, decorate the lawn of a small shop set back from the edges of the cobblestone road.  Twin walruses fashioned of elm hold a pine mermaid aloft in their tusks, the grinning passenger lies on her back with one hand on her stomach and the other hanging limp with a white seashell-shaped sign clutched in hand.  Fitfully burning lanterns are strategically placed along the lane to provide the best possible illumination for visitors.",
